3
00:01:43,290 --> 00:01:44,050
Hong Ri?

4
00:01:44,411 --> 00:01:45,451
Dia bukan Hong Ri.

5
00:01:46,531 --> 00:01:47,771
Mustahil.

6
00:01:47,851 --> 00:01:49,371
Ia sememangnya kuasa rohani Hong Ri.

7
00:01:49,650 --> 00:01:51,851
Itu hanya roh ketinggalan Hong Ri.

8
00:01:53,051 --> 00:01:54,131
Makhluk-makhluk biasa

9
00:01:54,410 --> 00:01:56,131
berani menceroboh
tempat pertapaan dewa sejati

10
00:01:56,611 --> 00:01:57,650
dan menghina keagungan dewa?

11
00:01:57,771 --> 00:01:58,851
Tinggalkan sini dengan segera!

12
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:00,291
Dewa Qilin,

13
00:02:00,650 --> 00:02:02,211
kami bukan sengaja menyinggung
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue.

14
00:02:02,810 --> 00:02:04,251
Cuma kewujudan Lembing Tai Chang

15
00:02:04,531 --> 00:02:05,691
membabitkan makhluk dunia tiga alam.

16
00:02:06,251 --> 00:02:07,571
Saya mewakili Istana Syurga
datang ambil lembing.

17
00:02:07,970 --> 00:02:09,810
Saya harap Dewa Qilin takkan menghalang.

18
00:02:10,051 --> 00:02:10,810
Naif!

19
00:02:11,211 --> 00:02:12,891
Lembing Tai Chang merupakan
senjata sakti dewa sejati,

20
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:14,571
hanya akan pilih tuan yang ditakdirkan.

21
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:16,330
Desas-desus tentang
kewujudan haiwan sakti Qilin

22
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:17,891
tersebar di tiga alam.

23
00:02:19,170 --> 00:02:21,810
Saya ingat dia masih hidup.

24
00:02:22,490 --> 00:02:24,571
Hari ini kewujudan
Qilin Api dan Lembing Tai Chang

25
00:02:25,371 --> 00:02:26,731
boleh menolong saya mengesahkan

26
00:02:27,330 --> 00:02:30,290
kalau-kalau Qing Mu ialah Bai Jue.

27
00:02:30,851 --> 00:02:31,970
Dewa Agung.

28
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:35,370
Rupa-rupanya,
awak bukan nak ambil lembing,

29
00:02:35,851 --> 00:02:36,690
tapi demi...

30
00:02:36,770 --> 00:02:37,851
Mereka memang dungu,

31
00:02:38,490 --> 00:02:39,651
senjata sakti dewa sejati

32
00:02:40,011 --> 00:02:42,370
bukannya boleh dikuasai oleh
siapa-siapa pun.

33
00:02:42,931 --> 00:02:44,130
Apa senjata sakti?

34
00:02:44,611 --> 00:02:46,611
Dah lama Alam Dewa Shang Gu ditutup.

35
00:02:47,130 --> 00:02:49,090
Sekarang, Istana Syurga paling berkuasa.

36
00:02:49,810 --> 00:02:50,611
Qilin Api,

37
00:02:50,810 --> 00:02:52,291
kalau awak serahkan Lembing Tai Chang,

38
00:02:52,651 --> 00:02:54,490
saya boleh lepaskan awak

39
00:02:54,730 --> 00:02:57,090
dan benarkan awak hidup
di Bukit Liao Wang.

40
00:02:57,730 --> 00:02:59,410
Anak kepada Naga Emas dan burung Phoenix

41
00:02:59,651 --> 00:03:01,090
berani berlagak di sini!

42
00:03:01,611 --> 00:03:02,571
Awak tak layak jadi

43
00:03:02,770 --> 00:03:03,571
tuan milik Lembing Tai Chang!

44
00:03:05,090 --> 00:03:05,851
Macam mana?

45
00:03:06,331 --> 00:03:07,331
Dia bukan Bo Xuan.

46
00:03:27,611 --> 00:03:28,651
Memang awak.

47
00:03:29,370 --> 00:03:30,571
Dah 60 ribu tahun berlalu,

48
00:03:31,011 --> 00:03:32,170
Alam Dewa pun dah musnah,

49
00:03:32,170 --> 00:03:33,251
tapi dia masih hidup.

50
00:03:34,011 --> 00:03:34,611
Alamak.

51
00:03:34,690 --> 00:03:35,730
Kuasa dewa Lembing Tai Chang
terlalu kuat,

52
00:03:35,851 --> 00:03:36,851
dah melebihi nadi rohani betara.

53
00:03:37,011 --> 00:03:37,770
Kalau teruskan begini...

54
00:03:38,811 --> 00:03:39,490
Hou Chi!

55
00:03:41,371 --> 00:03:42,091
Awak tak apa-apa?

56
00:03:42,530 --> 00:03:43,091
Feng Ran,

57
00:03:43,250 --> 00:03:44,291
kita mesti berikhtiar

58
00:03:44,451 --> 00:03:45,610
untuk memisahkan dia
dengan lembing dewa,

59
00:03:45,811 --> 00:03:47,610
kalau tidak, Qing Mu akan mati
akibat jasadnya meletup!

60
00:03:48,371 --> 00:03:49,490
Tahap kuasa semua orang

61
00:03:49,490 --> 00:03:50,490
bukan lawan lembing dewa.

62
00:03:50,811 --> 00:03:51,811
Bagaimana kita campur tangan?

63
00:03:53,171 --> 00:03:53,811
Abang ngah,

64
00:03:54,091 --> 00:03:55,610
cepat berikhtiar
untuk selamatkan Qing Mu.

65
00:03:55,970 --> 00:03:56,811
Kalau dia mati,

66
00:03:57,011 --> 00:03:57,970
saya juga takkan terus hidup.

67
00:03:58,371 --> 00:03:59,371
Qing Mu kawan sejati abang ngah.

68
00:03:59,931 --> 00:04:00,931
Abang ngah juga tak mahu dia
hadapi masalah.

69
00:04:01,371 --> 00:04:02,690
Namun, kuasa rohani amat kuat,

70
00:04:03,171 --> 00:04:04,050
apa yang patut buat?

71
00:04:08,371 --> 00:04:09,451
Hou Chi, cepat lihat.

72
00:04:09,970 --> 00:04:11,050
Qing Mu macam dah sedar.

73
00:04:11,451 --> 00:04:13,371
(Lembing ini merupakan senjata sakti
Dewa Sejati Bai Jue.)

74
00:04:13,890 --> 00:04:15,410
(Qilin ini merupakan haiwan sakti yang
mengawal lembing.)

75
00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:17,770
(Selain Dewa Sejati Bai Jue,)

76
00:04:17,970 --> 00:04:19,410
(mustahil Qilin mendekati orang lain.)

77
00:04:20,851 --> 00:04:21,811
(Adakah Qing Mu...)

78
00:04:41,690 --> 00:04:42,769
Gunung dan sungai masih ada,

79
00:04:43,849 --> 00:04:44,769
tapi Shang Gu,

80
00:04:46,250 --> 00:04:47,209
di mana awak?

81
00:04:52,769 --> 00:04:53,569
Hong Ri,

82
00:04:55,334 --> 00:04:56,774
Alam Dewa dah ditutup.

83
00:04:58,861 --> 00:05:00,342
Saya bawa roh awak
datang ke Alam Bawah.

84
00:05:01,782 --> 00:05:02,661
Mulai hari ini,

85
00:05:04,422 --> 00:05:05,861
awak tolong saya mengawal lembing dewa

86
00:05:07,422 --> 00:05:08,542
dan Bukit Liao Wang.

87
00:05:15,581 --> 00:05:18,301
Saya nak pergi cari Shang Gu.

88
00:05:19,581 --> 00:05:20,741
Sama ada berpuluh-puluh juta tahun

89
00:05:22,821 --> 00:05:23,941
atau beribu-ribu juta tahun,

90
00:05:26,581 --> 00:05:27,622
suatu hari nanti,

91
00:05:28,861 --> 00:05:30,182
Alam Dewa pasti akan wujud semula.

92
00:05:39,581 --> 00:05:40,502
Saya

93
00:05:41,821 --> 00:05:43,021
pasti akan cari dia sampai dapat.

94
00:05:51,502 --> 00:05:52,301
Shang Gu.

95
00:05:53,141 --> 00:05:54,021
Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

96
00:05:55,222 --> 00:05:56,102
Mengapa boleh...

97
00:05:56,741 --> 00:05:57,421
Hou Chi,

98
00:05:57,741 --> 00:05:58,581
apa yang dia cakap?

99
00:05:59,342 --> 00:06:00,622
Macam isu Alam Dewa.

100
00:06:01,222 --> 00:06:01,902
Dewa agung,

101
00:06:02,222 --> 00:06:02,981
mengapa dia

102
00:06:02,981 --> 00:06:04,222
tiada ingatan Dewa Agung Bai Jue?

103
00:06:05,102 --> 00:06:08,301
Kita berempat sama keturunan
dengan Tuhan.

104
00:06:09,222 --> 00:06:10,541
Biar jasad kita dah mati pun,

105
00:06:11,222 --> 00:06:13,342
juga akan lahir semula
di Altar Qian Kun.

106
00:06:14,541 --> 00:06:16,902
Kalau dia hanya tidur lena pada masa itu
dan bangun daripada tidur sekarang,

107
00:06:18,062 --> 00:06:20,021
mustahil embrionya juga tiada
dalam badannya.

108
00:06:21,182 --> 00:06:22,662
Hal ini tak begitu ringkas.

109
00:06:24,182 --> 00:06:25,461
Ketika Alam Dewa ditutup,

110
00:06:26,141 --> 00:06:27,902
apa cara yang dia guna

111
00:06:28,902 --> 00:06:31,222
sampai wujudnya jasad betara?

112
00:06:31,342 --> 00:06:32,141
Cepat lihat!

113
00:06:32,301 --> 00:06:33,861
Kuasa rohani pada badannya
dah jadi gelap.

114
00:06:34,141 --> 00:06:35,421
Lembing dewa nak mengaku tuannya?

115
00:06:36,182 --> 00:06:36,902
Kawan-kawan,

116
00:06:37,222 --> 00:06:38,222
jika lembing dewa mengaku tuannya,

117
00:06:38,421 --> 00:06:39,502
kita tak sempat merampas lembing lagi!

118
00:06:41,062 --> 00:06:42,062
Betara-betari dengar arahan!

119
00:06:42,461 --> 00:06:43,382
Lembing dewa ini tak boleh

120
00:06:43,622 --> 00:06:45,342
jatuh ke dalam tangan Puak Syaitan!

121
00:06:46,222 --> 00:06:46,942
Ya!

122
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,299
Zhao'er!

123
00:07:07,828 --> 00:07:09,627
Apa yang kita patut buat?

124
00:07:10,068 --> 00:07:11,388
Kalau mahu menangguk di air keruh,

125
00:07:11,988 --> 00:07:13,948
kita mesti menghuru-harakan keadaan.

126
00:07:14,268 --> 00:07:16,508
Asalkan Lembing Tai Chang jatuh
ke dalam tangan Qing Mu,

127
00:07:16,828 --> 00:07:18,388
barulah boleh kita tahu hal sebenar.

128
00:07:26,788 --> 00:07:27,467
Payung Yu Hua!

129
00:07:32,187 --> 00:07:33,068
Cari maut!

130
00:07:44,347 --> 00:07:45,828
Aura dalam badan Qing Mu kelam-kabut,

131
00:07:46,027 --> 00:07:47,027
agaknya dia sedang

132
00:07:47,027 --> 00:07:49,068
menggabungkan kuasa dewa
dengan Lembing Tai Chang.

133
00:07:49,867 --> 00:07:50,948
Nyawanya tak terancam.

134
00:07:50,948 --> 00:07:51,548
Feng Ran,

135
00:07:51,907 --> 00:07:53,307
kita mesti mengawal Qing Mu dengan baik.

136
00:07:53,627 --> 00:07:54,948
Setelah Qing Mu dapat Lembing Tai Chang

137
00:07:55,147 --> 00:07:55,948
dan sedarkan diri,

138
00:07:56,108 --> 00:07:57,228
kita tinggalkan sini serta-merta.

139
00:07:57,228 --> 00:07:58,268
Awak ambil berat terhadap dia,

140
00:07:58,388 --> 00:07:59,508
saya pasti tak benarkan dia tercedera.

141
00:07:59,948 --> 00:08:01,108
Jangan cakap begini.

142
00:08:01,948 --> 00:08:02,867
Dia berbudi pada saya,

143
00:08:03,187 --> 00:08:04,228
saya cuma hulurkan bantuan kepada dia.

144
00:08:04,668 --> 00:08:06,388
Cuma, kalau begini,

145
00:08:06,668 --> 00:08:07,467
Istana Qing Chi

146
00:08:07,788 --> 00:08:09,068
pasti akan terbabit.

147
00:08:09,068 --> 00:08:10,108
Mengapa fikir banyak?

148
00:08:10,108 --> 00:08:10,867
Saya melindungi dia.

149
00:08:11,228 --> 00:08:11,668
Tibalah masa

150
00:08:11,668 --> 00:08:12,988
menunjukkan kehebatan Istana Qing Chi.

151
00:08:19,427 --> 00:08:20,108
Zhao'er!

152
00:08:21,948 --> 00:08:23,747
Berani awak mencederakan saya!

153
00:08:23,948 --> 00:08:25,548
Saya mahu roh awak berkecai!

154
00:08:28,708 --> 00:08:29,388
Zhao'er.

155
00:08:29,587 --> 00:08:30,548
Tahap kuasa Qilin terlalu kuat,

156
00:08:30,988 --> 00:08:31,988
kita berdua bukan lawannya.

157
00:08:32,147 --> 00:08:33,548
Apa yang abang ngah takut?

158
00:08:33,907 --> 00:08:35,187
Saya ada Payung Yu Hua yang diberi
oleh Dewa Ibu,

159
00:08:35,347 --> 00:08:36,108
mustahil saya takkan berjaya!

160
00:08:39,467 --> 00:08:40,147
Zhao'er!

161
00:08:52,467 --> 00:08:53,268
Abang ngah.

162
00:09:14,788 --> 00:09:17,027
(Dewa agung,
Hong Ri terpaksa tinggalkan awak.)

163
00:09:17,708 --> 00:09:18,948
(Hong Ri rasa bersalah)

164
00:09:19,467 --> 00:09:20,467
(kerana gagal menyempurnakan tugasan.)

165
00:09:34,907 --> 00:09:36,508
Ini angkara siapa?

166
00:09:51,747 --> 00:09:53,147
Syaitan dan betara bertempur
merampas lembing

167
00:09:53,228 --> 00:09:54,668
sampai wujudnya konflik begini.

168
00:09:56,147 --> 00:09:57,268
Ini bukan pertempuran.

169
00:09:58,988 --> 00:10:00,148
Maksud Raja Syurga ialah...

170
00:10:07,028 --> 00:10:09,747
Kuasa dewa sejati
boleh menghuru-harakan keadaan.

171
00:10:11,348 --> 00:10:13,028
Ini kekuatan kuasa dewa sejati.

172
00:10:14,268 --> 00:10:15,627
Hou Chi, mengapa awak tak apa-apa?

173
00:10:17,722 --> 00:10:18,802
Kuasa rohani dewi amat hebat,

174
00:10:19,281 --> 00:10:20,401
tolong melindungi saya.

175
00:10:23,562 --> 00:10:24,242
Qing Mu!

176
00:10:24,802 --> 00:10:26,242
Memandangkan lembing dewa
dah pilih awak sebagai tuannya,

177
00:10:26,802 --> 00:10:28,641
awak pasti boleh jadi dewa atasan.

178
00:10:29,122 --> 00:10:30,682
Tadi, saya dah habiskan tenaga

179
00:10:30,922 --> 00:10:32,321
tolong awak bunuh Qilin Api!

180
00:10:32,562 --> 00:10:33,761
Zhao'er, jangan cakap sembarangan!

181
00:10:34,682 --> 00:10:36,002
Kamu mencerobohi
kawasan pertapaan saya,

182
00:10:36,521 --> 00:10:38,002
membunuh haiwan sakti saya
yang melindungi bukit ini.

183
00:10:38,602 --> 00:10:39,562
Kesalahan awak tak boleh dimaafkan.

184
00:10:44,042 --> 00:10:44,761
Zhao'er!

185
00:10:45,042 --> 00:10:46,401
(Orang itu boleh memasuki
fikiran Qing Mu,)

186
00:10:46,761 --> 00:10:48,122
(pastinya satu roh yang tiada fikiran.)

187
00:10:48,761 --> 00:10:49,881
(Namun, kuasa rohaninya amat kuat,)

188
00:10:49,881 --> 00:10:50,761
(tak boleh merangsang dia.)

189
00:10:51,362 --> 00:10:53,002
(Saya hanya boleh
mengadu nasib sendiri.)

190
00:10:53,401 --> 00:10:54,602
Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

191
00:10:57,682 --> 00:11:00,802
Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

192
00:11:06,162 --> 00:11:06,922
Shang Gu.

193
00:11:11,922 --> 00:11:12,682
Hou Chi!

194
00:11:25,383 --> 00:11:26,143
Saya dah balik.

195
00:11:29,943 --> 00:11:30,782
Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

196
00:11:31,863 --> 00:11:32,703
Adakah awak tercedera?

197
00:11:34,462 --> 00:11:35,303
Awak kenal saya?

198
00:11:36,823 --> 00:11:37,782
Saya bukan saja kenal awak,

199
00:11:39,063 --> 00:11:40,183
tapi dah lama kita berkenalan,

200
00:11:41,063 --> 00:11:42,222
lebih lama daripada kewujudan
gunung dan sungai.

201
00:11:43,782 --> 00:11:45,422
Saya tak pernah lupakan awak.

202
00:11:47,662 --> 00:11:50,022
Hou Chi, awak ini keji!

203
00:11:51,491 --> 00:11:54,851
♪Ia samar-samar, namun masih jelas♪

204
00:11:54,982 --> 00:11:55,703
Dewa agung,

205
00:11:56,303 --> 00:11:57,582
saya tak reti ajar anak.

206
00:11:58,143 --> 00:12:01,383
Anak saya yang bersalah kerana
mencederakan roh Hong Ri.

207
00:12:01,902 --> 00:12:04,222
Tolong maafkan anak saya dengan
berikan muka kepada saya

208
00:12:04,383 --> 00:12:05,263
dan Wu Huan.

209
00:12:05,986 --> 00:12:07,950
♪Selepas terserempak dengan awak♪

210
00:12:07,982 --> 00:12:08,782
Dewa Agung Bai Jue.

211
00:12:09,503 --> 00:12:11,863
Tolong lepaskan mereka berdua.

212
00:12:12,063 --> 00:12:13,582
Kalau mereka mati dalam tangan awak,

213
00:12:13,982 --> 00:12:16,863
kelak, Qing Mu tiada maruah
berada di tiga alam lagi.

214
00:12:17,703 --> 00:12:18,503
Shang Gu.

215
00:12:21,544 --> 00:12:23,971
♪Dengarlah♪

216
00:12:24,331 --> 00:12:27,331
♪Sama-sama ada telepati♪

217
00:12:28,051 --> 00:12:30,971
♪Dekati♪

218
00:12:31,451 --> 00:12:35,011
♪Cakap secara ringkas♪

219
00:12:35,611 --> 00:12:38,500
♪Kalau tiada pemandangan baik begini♪

220
00:12:38,542 --> 00:12:39,222
Hou Chi!

221
00:12:39,571 --> 00:12:42,331
♪Semoga awak♪

222
00:12:42,411 --> 00:12:46,371
♪Ikut♪

223
00:12:52,954 --> 00:12:53,714
Sudahlah.

224
00:12:54,473 --> 00:12:56,514
Memandangkan Lembing Tai Chang
dah pilih tuannya,

225
00:12:56,834 --> 00:12:58,634
hal ini dah berakhir.

226
00:12:59,274 --> 00:13:01,353
Kita balik ke bukit betara
masing-masing.

227
00:13:02,113 --> 00:13:03,274
Puak Syaitan

228
00:13:03,593 --> 00:13:04,714
tak dibenarkan berada di Alam Kayangan.

229
00:13:05,634 --> 00:13:06,473
Ya.

230
00:13:07,954 --> 00:13:10,233
Jian'er, bawa Zhao'er balik.

231
00:13:10,634 --> 00:13:11,434
Ya, Dewa Bapa.

232
00:13:14,913 --> 00:13:15,593
Tuanku,

233
00:13:15,793 --> 00:13:17,434
Betara Qing Mu ialah...

234
00:13:18,194 --> 00:13:19,074
Tiada tenaga embrio

235
00:13:19,233 --> 00:13:21,274
Dewa Agung Bai Jue di dalam badannya.

236
00:13:21,834 --> 00:13:23,074
Mereka cuma mirip saja.

237
00:13:25,933 --> 00:13:27,214
Sebelum ini kita berjumpa,

238
00:13:27,214 --> 00:13:28,413
awak masih budak kecil.

239
00:13:28,973 --> 00:13:31,733
Tak sangka awak dah besar.

240
00:13:32,134 --> 00:13:33,613
Kalau Dewa Bapa awak balik,

241
00:13:33,613 --> 00:13:34,613
dia pasti amat gembira.

242
00:13:37,173 --> 00:13:38,454
Hari jadi saya selama 60 ribu tahun ini

243
00:13:38,933 --> 00:13:39,582
